        <h3>Helen Williamson, Author</h3>
        <p>
            {{#markdown}}
                Helen Lorrain Williamson was born in Holywood, Northern Ireland. She received her B.A. and M.A. from Trinity College in Dublin, Ireland. For many years she taught creative writing in
                Charlottesville, Virginia, where she lives with her husband. She is the author of *Tales from Balladhoon*, *A Pineapple Dream and Other Nonsense*, *Higgledy-Piggledy Thoughts*, *I Just
                Met A Dinosaur!*, *Adventures In Dinglewood*, and *Tales from Balladhoon* (2).
            {{/markdown}}
        </p>
        <p>
